laims for existing (stopping wars and atrocities). But it does manage to bully peaceful nations into giving up healthy values in favor of globalist decay.\n\nWe've already withdrawn $15 billion dollars from the UN... I say, take the other $2 billion and cut our membership out entirely. Let this wretched organization rot and die. And no more money for the EU either.", "author": "MAGA9428", "created": 1774988592171, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "snoopy3210", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "We should completely withdraw from the United Nations and let it burn...", "last_comment_created": 1775017983605, "content": "<p>The United Nations is the biggest instrument of globalism. It plays an active role in enforcing liberal values on countries and treating traditional values as a problem to be solved. It never actually fulfills the purpose it claims for existing (stopping wars and atrocities). But it does manage to bully peaceful nations into giving up healthy values in favor of globalist decay.</p>\n<p>We've already withdrawn $15 billion dollars from the UN... I say, take the other $2 billion and cut our membership out entirely. Let this wretched organization rot and die. And no more money for the EU either.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 9, "score_up": 223, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZ8Kc1QM", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin